{Speech 2 Answer 20}{}{You look kind of down, Dusty. Something wrong?}
{Speech 2 Answer 31}{}{Dusty, about your "party"...}
{Speech 2 Answer 26}{}{Dusty, about your "party"...}
{Speech 2 Answer 26*}{}{Dusty, about your "party"...}
{Speech 2 Answer 26**}{}{Dusty, about your "party"...}
{Speech 2 Answer 65}{}{Hey, Dusty! They say bartenders never miss a thing. Mind answering a question?}
{Speech 2 Answer 200}{}{Listen, I wanted@sex@|| to ask, have you seen a certain man?@@Listen, I wanted@sex@|| to find out, have you heard anything about a certain man?@@I'm looking for a certain man, heard anything about him?}
